      "text": "- Auth Token Forward \nBetween all the Microsevrice for - Authentication \n- Every API call is RBAC which is Encoded \nin the AccessToken - Authorization \n- Every Payload is Validated using Pydantic\n  which is - Validation",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "- Auth Token Forward \nBetween all the Microsevrice for - Authentication \n- Every API call is RBAC which is Encoded \nin the AccessToken - Authorization \n- Every Payload is Validated using Pydantic\n  which is - Validation",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
